abstract: TWENTY-ONE years is a sufficient span of time for  a fashion event to become an institution. That's how long Ohrbach's has been skimming the cream of the European couture fashion showings and offering its reproductions by Seventh Avenue manufacturers.

abstract: SUMMIT, N.J., Sept. 17-- Diane Ward rode Smoke Rise Stable's Southern Comfort to the open jumper championship at the Watchung Hunter Horse Show today.
